title: Household rent to income ratio in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2018 - 2019 , by region
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 14 different Regions on X-axis for 2 groups Oct' 18, and Oct '19. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
